====Teotihuacano====
[[Teotihuacan]] was a city built in the [[Valley of Mexico]], containing some of the largest [[Mesoamerican pyramid|pyramidal structures]] built in the [[pre-Columbian]] [[The Americas|Americas]]. Established around 200 BCE, the city fell between the 7th and 8th century CE. Teotihuacan has numerous well-preserved [[mural]]s.<!-- (Add more about masks) -->

